  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Troops seize 25 kilos of rice",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "An army soldier was arrested yesterday (30) by the Monaragala police in connection with the theft of 25 kilos of rice loaded in a three-wheeler in Monaragala town.",
        "A resident of Obbegoda, the owner of the three-wheeler, had complained to the police that someone had stolen 25 kilos of rice from a three-wheeler while it was stopped in the center of Monaragala on the 25th.",
        "The Monaragala police, who conducted an investigation into the incident through the nearby CCTV camera footage, arrested a thirty-three-year-old army sergeant working at Kurunegala Boyagane military camp, a resident of Moneragala Hulandawa South Gemunupura area.",
        "Monaragala Headquarters Police Inspector PS Charminda Sanjeeva is conducting investigations."
      ],
